  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin powder, red chili powder, and salt. Let the spices roast for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chopped onion, ginger, and garlic. Cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the palak leaves and 1 cup of water. Boil until the leaves are tender.",
    "Add the paneer and red pepper paste. Mix well.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "Add black pepper and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve hot with naan or rice."
